1
00:00:10,960 --> 00:00:13,420
♪The maple mark on your skin♪

2
00:00:14,230 --> 00:00:17,040
♪The only proof we exist♪

3
00:00:18,210 --> 00:00:21,450
♪I stole you back from destiny♪

4
00:00:21,560 --> 00:00:24,430
♪But can I redeem myself♪

5
00:00:24,430 --> 00:00:26,540
♪I don't care what fate foretells♪

6
00:00:26,750 --> 00:00:30,330
♪Or how rough the road may be♪

7
00:00:30,340 --> 00:00:33,280
♪Stay, I'll fight for you♪

8
00:00:33,610 --> 00:00:37,660
♪That's all I'll ever do♪

9
00:00:37,760 --> 00:00:39,890
♪If life is just a show♪

10
00:00:39,890 --> 00:00:42,650
♪I'll stay with you till the end♪

11
00:00:42,650 --> 00:00:44,980
♪I'm scared we'll wake up alone♪

12
00:00:44,980 --> 00:00:47,960
♪So don't let this dream end♪

13
00:00:47,960 --> 00:00:52,420
♪In my bones, in my heart♪

14
00:00:52,420 --> 00:00:54,100
♪I know I'll have to leave♪

15
00:00:54,100 --> 00:00:55,670
♪You must not leave my side♪

16
00:00:55,670 --> 00:00:57,260
♪No place can hold us in♪

17
00:00:57,260 --> 00:01:01,910
♪Not when it's you and me♪

18
00:01:06,890 --> 00:01:10,400
♪Forever♪

19
00:01:11,490 --> 00:01:15,250
♪In my soul♪

20
00:01:17,260 --> 00:01:23,300
=This Palace Maid Isn't Very Calm=
=Episode 17=

21
00:01:28,400 --> 00:01:29,950
Your Majesty, bad news!

22
00:01:30,920 --> 00:01:32,710
Why are you in such a panic?

23
00:01:33,000 --> 00:01:34,710
News has come from the 14th Prince.

24
00:01:34,840 --> 00:01:37,200
They say the 14th Prince
has also caught pox rash.

25
00:01:38,120 --> 00:01:39,000
What?

26
00:01:39,480 --> 00:01:40,760
What is the situation now?

27
00:01:40,920 --> 00:01:43,040
His residence has been locked down.

28
00:01:43,120 --> 00:01:44,640
All servants who contacted him

29
00:01:44,640 --> 00:01:46,040
have been forcibly quarantined.

30
00:01:46,120 --> 00:01:47,590
It was ordered by Miss Ye Jin.

31
00:01:47,640 --> 00:01:49,840
Now Miss Ye Jin is staying with him

32
00:01:49,840 --> 00:01:50,950
and taking care of him personally.

33
00:01:53,040 --> 00:01:54,430
Ye Jin has done well.

34
00:01:56,070 --> 00:01:57,710
The top priority now

35
00:01:57,870 --> 00:01:59,920
is to stop smallpox from spreading.

36
00:02:00,560 --> 00:02:01,840
Ye Jin knows medicine.

37
00:02:01,840 --> 00:02:03,510
With her taking care of him,

38
00:02:03,510 --> 00:02:04,640
I am at ease.

39
00:02:05,000 --> 00:02:05,950
Deliver my order.

40
00:02:06,200 --> 00:02:08,520
Order all imperial physicians
to enter the palace.

41
00:02:08,750 --> 00:02:09,590
Yes.

42
00:02:46,600 --> 00:02:48,460
(Hearing the Prince is ill,
I made some snacks for you.)

43
00:02:50,800 --> 00:02:52,150
Lady Xiao, you are thoughtful.

44
00:02:53,000 --> 00:02:53,840
Your Highness.

45
00:02:53,910 --> 00:02:55,630
You are in for a treat today.

46
00:02:56,430 --> 00:02:57,270
Your Highness?

47
00:03:02,310 --> 00:03:03,150
Your Highness.

48
00:03:04,930 --> 00:03:06,120
Why is he burning up so badly?

49
00:03:06,710 --> 00:03:07,550
Eunuch Fu.

50
00:03:07,580 --> 00:03:08,630
Bring a basin of cold water.

51
00:03:08,630 --> 00:03:09,470
Yes.

52
00:03:10,240 --> 00:03:11,080
Your Highness.

53
00:03:24,080 --> 00:03:25,150
I can't stand the itching.

54
00:03:25,150 --> 00:03:26,400
Alright, I know.

55
00:03:26,520 --> 00:03:27,400
Hold on.

56
00:03:30,020 --> 00:03:30,870
Eunuch Fu.

57
00:03:30,870 --> 00:03:32,000
Hold His Highness's hands.

58
00:03:34,870 --> 00:03:36,000
Hold on, Your Highness.

59
00:03:39,150 --> 00:03:39,990
Your Highness!

60
00:03:40,150 --> 00:03:40,990
Itching.

61
00:03:41,000 --> 00:03:41,840
Forgive me, Your Highness.

62
00:03:41,840 --> 00:03:43,000
Go fetch a rope.

63
00:03:43,080 --> 00:03:43,920
Yes.

64
00:03:48,190 --> 00:03:49,030
Itching.

65
00:03:51,680 --> 00:03:52,680
Hold his hands.

66
00:04:02,750 --> 00:04:05,000
No, we must go to the Imperial Clinic.

67
00:04:05,000 --> 00:04:06,560
Get another prescription for itching.

68
00:04:09,120 --> 00:04:10,000
Don't go.

69
00:04:10,840 --> 00:04:11,680
Stay.

70
00:04:12,120 --> 00:04:13,400
Talk to me.

71
00:04:13,840 --> 00:04:14,680
About what?

72
00:04:15,150 --> 00:04:15,990
Just tell me

73
00:04:16,600 --> 00:04:17,830
about your hometown.

74
00:04:18,630 --> 00:04:19,870
My hometown?

75
00:04:20,800 --> 00:04:22,680
My hometown is dull beyond words.

76
00:04:22,950 --> 00:04:24,190
Then tell me about...

77
00:04:25,070 --> 00:04:26,750
about that

78
00:04:27,430 --> 00:04:28,560
young man from your hometown.

79
00:04:31,190 --> 00:04:32,750
You still remember him?

80
00:04:34,070 --> 00:04:34,910
Fine.

81
00:04:35,750 --> 00:04:37,000
It is not that I cannot say.

82
00:04:38,310 --> 00:04:39,390
His name is

83
00:04:40,830 --> 00:04:41,800
An Jingyu.

84
00:04:41,830 --> 00:04:43,000
And he was

85
00:04:43,000 --> 00:04:44,950
extremely handsome and charming.

86
00:04:46,560 --> 00:04:47,720
Then

87
00:04:47,950 --> 00:04:49,480
he became famous overnight.

88
00:04:49,830 --> 00:04:51,720
With his final concert,

89
00:04:51,720 --> 00:04:54,430
he secured his place
as the top musician.

90
00:04:54,510 --> 00:04:55,560
He went from

91
00:04:56,040 --> 00:04:57,390
a nobody

92
00:04:57,870 --> 00:05:00,040
to the top musician.

93
00:05:01,000 --> 00:05:02,310
That's amazing.

94
00:05:02,310 --> 00:05:03,150
Mm.

95
00:05:03,600 --> 00:05:04,560
But...

96
00:05:04,800 --> 00:05:06,510
what do you mean

97
00:05:06,510 --> 00:05:08,630
"Group variety made him famous and
music variety does the rest?"

98
00:05:08,950 --> 00:05:11,480
I don't understand these words.

99
00:05:13,190 --> 00:05:14,360
It's normal you haven't.

100
00:05:14,560 --> 00:05:16,120
They're slang from my hometown.

101
00:05:16,510 --> 00:05:17,920
It's okay you don't get it.

102
00:05:18,120 --> 00:05:20,390
Your dialect is strange.

103
00:05:20,570 --> 00:05:22,160
Stranger than
the Classic of Mountains and Seas.

104
00:05:22,920 --> 00:05:25,720
And about "fandom,

105
00:05:26,600 --> 00:05:27,720
fan voting,

106
00:05:28,120 --> 00:05:29,360
fan support,"

107
00:05:29,360 --> 00:05:30,680
what do they mean?

108
00:05:31,070 --> 00:05:34,310
He became popular outside his fanbase
because of a drama?

109
00:05:34,720 --> 00:05:35,870
What's a drama?

110
00:05:36,040 --> 00:05:39,160
His crying scenes were bad,

111
00:05:39,190 --> 00:05:41,120
but his looks made him
popular outside his fanbase.

112
00:05:41,190 --> 00:05:43,510
What does "outside his fanbase" mean?

113
00:05:43,510 --> 00:05:44,950
It's nothing.

114
00:05:45,270 --> 00:05:46,510
I was just so sleepy

115
00:05:46,510 --> 00:05:48,160
that I rambled.

116
00:05:48,160 --> 00:05:49,510
I don't know why.

117
00:05:51,160 --> 00:05:54,390
Your ramblings
always make sense somehow.

118
00:05:54,510 --> 00:05:55,350
Your Highness.

119
00:05:56,830 --> 00:05:58,000
Your fever is gone.

120
00:05:58,430 --> 00:05:59,430
It's getting late.

121
00:05:59,430 --> 00:06:00,270
Get some sleep.

122
00:06:22,750 --> 00:06:23,870
You're awake, Your Highness.

123
00:06:26,100 --> 00:06:27,190
Your Highness, how do you feel?

124
00:06:30,040 --> 00:06:30,950
Your Highness, your face...

125
00:06:32,190 --> 00:06:33,360
My face?

126
00:06:40,160 --> 00:06:41,480
The spots are gone?

127
00:06:45,560 --> 00:06:46,630
In just a few days,

128
00:06:48,270 --> 00:06:49,360
I've fully recovered.

129
00:06:49,800 --> 00:06:50,720
No.

130
00:06:51,160 --> 00:06:52,600
It shouldn't be this fast.

131
00:06:52,720 --> 00:06:53,720
What's wrong?

132
00:06:55,240 --> 00:06:56,870
If it were smallpox,

133
00:06:57,680 --> 00:06:59,430
you couldn't recover this quickly.

134
00:07:00,430 --> 00:07:02,560
Your symptoms are more like chickenpox.

135
00:07:02,950 --> 00:07:04,240
Commonly called water pox.

136
00:07:04,240 --> 00:07:06,310
Its early symptoms are like smallpox,

137
00:07:06,310 --> 00:07:07,430
but it's mild.

138
00:07:07,430 --> 00:07:08,950
It heals in about seven days.

139
00:07:09,430 --> 00:07:10,720
So that means...

140
00:07:11,430 --> 00:07:12,630
I won't die?

141
00:07:14,270 --> 00:07:15,720
You won't.

142
00:07:18,750 --> 00:07:20,310
(If that's true,)

143
00:07:20,430 --> 00:07:22,480
(then much can be made of it.)

144
00:07:26,560 --> 00:07:27,600
Greetings, Noble Lady.

145
00:07:28,040 --> 00:07:29,040
Take care, Sister.

146
00:07:44,420 --> 00:07:46,860
(The smallpox incident
was a setup by Consort Lan.)

147
00:07:46,870 --> 00:07:47,920
This is

148
00:07:47,920 --> 00:07:49,430
Ye Jin's notes.

149
00:07:51,040 --> 00:07:52,190
(The smallpox incident)

150
00:07:52,310 --> 00:07:53,830
(was a setup by Consort Lan.)

151
00:07:54,120 --> 00:07:56,190
(She used it to make Consort Duan
fall from favor.)

152
00:07:56,360 --> 00:07:57,310
(After this,)

153
00:07:57,310 --> 00:07:58,950
(she will rule the harem alone.)

154
00:07:59,240 --> 00:08:01,920
(She's one step away
from being Empress.)

155
00:08:02,270 --> 00:08:03,510
(She's arrogant.)

156
00:08:03,510 --> 00:08:04,430
(If she gains full power,)

157
00:08:04,430 --> 00:08:06,240
(life in the harem will be hard.)

158
00:08:07,120 --> 00:08:08,160
(I have a plan)

159
00:08:08,270 --> 00:08:10,000
(to help you rise with the tide)

160
00:08:10,000 --> 00:08:11,310
(and rival her.)

161
00:08:11,750 --> 00:08:13,430
(But this plan is a gamble.)

162
00:08:13,630 --> 00:08:15,040
(Win and you'll rise high.)

163
00:08:15,310 --> 00:08:16,800
(Lose and you'll be ruined.)

164
00:08:17,040 --> 00:08:19,120
(Will you take the risk?)

165
00:08:40,240 --> 00:08:42,750
Press harder for this stroke.

166
00:08:43,030 --> 00:08:43,870
Alright.

167
00:08:45,510 --> 00:08:48,000
Have you learned the characters
I taught today?

168
00:08:54,030 --> 00:08:55,720
Mother, let me recite a poem for you.

169
00:08:56,240 --> 00:08:58,320
Thread from a loving mother's hands

170
00:08:58,550 --> 00:09:00,270
becomes the clothes
for her traveling son.

171
00:09:00,550 --> 00:09:02,790
She sews tightly before he leaves,

172
00:09:02,910 --> 00:09:04,720
fearing his late return.

173
00:09:05,150 --> 00:09:07,200
Who says my heart
like a blade of grass

174
00:09:07,550 --> 00:09:09,320
could repay her love's
gentle beams of spring sun?

175
00:09:25,000 --> 00:09:27,840
(Imperial Edict)
By the Emperor's divine order,

176
00:09:27,840 --> 00:09:29,720
Yun Tianci, Prefect of Huzhou,

177
00:09:29,870 --> 00:09:31,550
as a court official,

178
00:09:31,550 --> 00:09:32,750
secretly colluded with Prince Wu,

179
00:09:32,750 --> 00:09:33,910
harboring disloyal designs.

180
00:09:34,080 --> 00:09:35,320
The evidence is solid.

181
00:09:35,320 --> 00:09:36,840
He is dismissed and investigated today.

182
00:09:36,840 --> 00:09:38,270
Confiscate the property
and execute him.

183
00:09:38,790 --> 00:09:39,840
By Imperial Decree.

184
00:09:41,720 --> 00:09:42,870
All my life,

185
00:09:43,200 --> 00:09:44,720
I've been loyal to His Majesty.

186
00:09:44,720 --> 00:09:46,120
Never disloyal.

187
00:09:46,360 --> 00:09:47,200
You...

188
00:09:47,270 --> 00:09:48,910
You're slandering me!

189
00:09:48,910 --> 00:09:50,510
Framing a loyal official!

190
00:09:50,510 --> 00:09:51,440
Insolence!

191
00:09:51,790 --> 00:09:52,630
Guards!

192
00:09:52,720 --> 00:09:53,560
Seize him!

193
00:09:54,670 --> 00:09:55,510
My Lord!

194
00:09:55,720 --> 00:09:56,560
My Lord!

195
00:09:59,120 --> 00:09:59,960
My Lady!

196
00:10:00,750 --> 00:10:01,590
My Lady!

197
00:10:02,480 --> 00:10:03,870
My Lady!

198
00:10:04,600 --> 00:10:05,480
You...

199
00:10:05,630 --> 00:10:07,440
I'll fight you to the end!

200
00:10:23,360 --> 00:10:24,600
My father was wronged.

201
00:10:25,320 --> 00:10:26,600
My mother died tragically.

202
00:10:27,390 --> 00:10:30,600
The Lan clan is to blame.

203
00:10:31,440 --> 00:10:33,150
Anyone can be Empress,

204
00:10:33,550 --> 00:10:34,910
except Consort Lan.

205
00:10:35,750 --> 00:10:37,080
She must not be Empress.

206
00:10:39,270 --> 00:10:41,480
I came to the palace
with nothing but this one life.

207
00:10:42,630 --> 00:10:44,000
Why should I fear trying?

208
00:10:57,750 --> 00:10:58,750
(If you'll take the risk,)

209
00:10:58,750 --> 00:11:00,790
(then do as I tell you.)

210
00:11:01,120 --> 00:11:02,200
(Remember, be cautious.)

211
00:11:02,320 --> 00:11:04,000
(Don't let anyone catch you.)

212
00:11:25,480 --> 00:11:28,600
I heard refugees
outside the city are settled.

213
00:11:28,600 --> 00:11:30,150
The outbreak in the city
is easing as well.

214
00:11:30,360 --> 00:11:33,000
Only Consort Duan and the 14th Prince
are ill in the palace.

215
00:11:33,000 --> 00:11:34,360
No new cases.

216
00:11:34,720 --> 00:11:35,560
Now,

217
00:11:35,870 --> 00:11:37,120
they're out of danger.

218
00:11:37,390 --> 00:11:39,670
At last, we've pulled through.

219
00:11:40,240 --> 00:11:41,670
Thanks to your prescription.

220
00:11:42,200 --> 00:11:43,510
I dare not claim the credit.

221
00:11:43,870 --> 00:11:46,270
It's all thanks to
Your Majesty's strategy.

222
00:11:50,870 --> 00:11:52,510
Your Majesty, Your Ladyship.

223
00:11:52,630 --> 00:11:54,910
Someone from Consort Duan's palace says

224
00:11:54,910 --> 00:11:56,600
Consort Duan is agitated,

225
00:11:56,630 --> 00:11:57,630
and it's harmed the baby.

226
00:11:58,330 --> 00:11:59,390
Did you send for the physician?

227
00:11:59,390 --> 00:12:00,550
Yes.

228
00:12:01,000 --> 00:12:01,870
Only...

229
00:12:01,870 --> 00:12:03,270
I heard from the palace maids

230
00:12:03,320 --> 00:12:04,840
that Consort Duan has quite a temper,

231
00:12:04,960 --> 00:12:06,750
and all the servants are frightened.

232
00:12:08,600 --> 00:12:11,960
It is said expectant mothers
must avoid unrest of mind.

233
00:12:16,440 --> 00:12:17,550
I'll go see her first.

234
00:12:22,240 --> 00:12:24,270
You're all useless!

235
00:12:24,630 --> 00:12:26,390
Everyone is a sycophants.

236
00:12:27,150 --> 00:12:28,870
When I ran the harem,

237
00:12:29,870 --> 00:12:30,960
all these things

238
00:12:31,270 --> 00:12:33,750
were given to me first!

239
00:12:36,240 --> 00:12:38,790
Now she runs the harem,

240
00:12:39,750 --> 00:12:42,120
she's making things hard for me!

241
00:12:51,080 --> 00:12:51,920
Your Majesty.

242
00:12:58,720 --> 00:12:59,560
Your Majesty.

243
00:13:00,090 --> 00:13:01,440
You've finally come.

244
00:13:02,550 --> 00:13:04,550
You must uphold justice for me.

245
00:13:05,720 --> 00:13:06,560
Shrew.

246
00:13:09,510 --> 00:13:10,350
Your Majesty!

247
00:13:23,120 --> 00:13:23,960
Sixi.

248
00:13:24,320 --> 00:13:25,630
Why are you pacing?

249
00:13:25,840 --> 00:13:27,000
You're annoying me.

250
00:13:34,720 --> 00:13:35,560
Your Majesty,

251
00:13:35,720 --> 00:13:36,750
it is me.

252
00:13:37,320 --> 00:13:38,200
Noble Lady Hui.

253
00:13:45,750 --> 00:13:47,870
I have not seen Your Majesty
for so long.

254
00:13:47,870 --> 00:13:48,750
I missed you dearly.

255
00:13:49,240 --> 00:13:52,150
So I made tonic soup to comfort you.

256
00:13:54,320 --> 00:13:55,190
Your Majesty,

257
00:13:55,360 --> 00:13:57,080
how did your hand get hurt?

258
00:13:58,080 --> 00:13:58,920
It's nothing.

259
00:13:59,200 --> 00:14:00,040
Just a small injury.

260
00:14:00,790 --> 00:14:02,090
Even a minor injury,

261
00:14:02,230 --> 00:14:03,360
the Imperial Heir is injured as well.

262
00:14:04,780 --> 00:14:05,620
Eunuch Sixi.

263
00:14:05,900 --> 00:14:07,440
Please bring some ointment.

264
00:14:07,750 --> 00:14:08,590
Yes.

265
00:14:53,610 --> 00:14:56,050
♪I am but an outsider♪

266
00:14:56,090 --> 00:14:58,250
♪Yet something drags me deeper♪

267
00:14:58,490 --> 00:15:02,530
♪Outwit the world
but not the way we meet♪

268
00:15:02,530 --> 00:15:06,770
♪Splendid blooms line deadly ground♪

269
00:15:11,050 --> 00:15:14,290
♪Life's a phantom, yet I find you♪

270
00:15:14,450 --> 00:15:17,850
♪In a world of lies,
you're all that's clear♪

271
00:15:17,850 --> 00:15:20,370
♪I know how this story ends♪

272
00:15:20,370 --> 00:15:24,930
♪I still want what's in your eyes♪

273
00:15:25,250 --> 00:15:29,370
♪Truth or lie—I can't tell♪

274
00:15:34,330 --> 00:15:37,650
♪Truth or lie—I can't tell♪

275
00:15:37,650 --> 00:15:40,930
♪So familiar, yet out of reach♪

276
00:15:41,130 --> 00:15:44,210
♪A history that no one can search♪

277
00:15:44,450 --> 00:15:47,730
♪Like you drift in from another star♪

278
00:15:47,770 --> 00:15:49,530
♪I am but an outsider♪

279
00:15:49,530 --> 00:15:51,770
♪Yet something drags me deeper♪

280
00:15:51,770 --> 00:15:55,810
♪Outwit the world
but not the way we meet♪

281
00:15:55,810 --> 00:16:00,490
♪Splendid blooms line deadly ground♪

282
00:16:04,410 --> 00:16:07,810
♪Life's a phantom, yet I find you♪

283
00:16:07,810 --> 00:16:11,170
♪In a world of lies,
you're all that's clear♪

284
00:16:11,170 --> 00:16:13,650
♪I know how this story ends♪

285
00:16:13,650 --> 00:16:17,810
♪I still want what's in your eyes♪

286
00:16:17,810 --> 00:16:21,090
♪When it's over and I'm gone♪

287
00:16:21,090 --> 00:16:24,890
♪Please forget me and move on♪

288
00:16:24,890 --> 00:16:31,130
♪Just let this absurd dream fade♪

289
00:16:34,290 --> 00:16:42,650
♪Snow hides our tracks♪

290
00:16:46,210 --> 00:16:55,930
♪When do I finally wake♪
